title: Beef vegetable stir fry with egg noodles
ingredients: ['1 tablespoon olive oil', '1 onion, finely chopped', '250g beef steak fillet, sliced', '1 carrot, coarsely grated', '1/2 red pepper, cut into strips', '2 tomatoes, chopped', '1 (2.5cm) root ginger, minced', '1 tablespoon Worcestershire sauce', '2 tablespoon soy sauce', '1 teaspoon Chinese five spice', '250g fresh egg noodles', '1 teaspoon fresh chopped parsley']
